references: Related: CF 271363. Superseding: Ord 99490, Ord 99575, Ord 1000762, Ord 100426.
summary: AN ORDINANCE establishing, modifying and abrogating certain positions in the Seattle-King County Public Health, Fire and Water Departments and in the Municipal Court; providing compensation therefor, and superseding the 1971 Budget (Ordinance 99490) and the 1971 Salary Ordinance (99575) as amended by Ordinances 100072 and 100426 insofar as in conflict.
